definitions.definition: The disaccharide sugar of milk and dairy products, C 12 H 22 O 11 , a product of glucose and galactose used as a food and in medicinal compounds.

main_definition: ( biochemistry ) The disaccharide sugar of milk and dairy products, C 12 H 22 O 11 , a product of glucose and galactose used as a food and in medicinal compounds.
